Package com.example.syntaxeventlottery

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.example.syntaxeventlottery.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Entrant
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a general user within the Event Lottery System. The User class stores various details about a user, including their ID, device code, email, phone number, profile photo, roles, associated facility, and location.
